N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 373.11 - Plan administration

State Regulations

The plan shall be administered by the trustee. The trustee
shall have the same authority to administer the plan as exists for the system. The trustee may delegate any or all of the trustee's administrative
authority. Notes
